_sText:
= Surf_Ebony by Sid =

Sequel to the hugely popular surf_ivory, I wanted to make a map to run parallel with it, thus creating Ebony. I started working a year ago this month, but with a relaxed approach. I'm very happy with the surf and theme, and I hope you all enjoy playing!

Tier 2 Linear
4 Bonuses, featuring the works of donkey, S a g a n and not_a_zombie

5k maxvel, autohop off.
